V 933
tooltip format. current source:

<html><head><head/><body>
<b>How to add a friend: </b><p>
<i>Add Non-Sticky-Modus: <b>Repleo Exchange</b></i><p><ol>
<li>Obtain the key from your friend. Paste it and press the Add button.</li>
<li>Copy your Repleo for this friend from the context menu in the Participants table of the Chat tab.</li>
<li>Send this Repleo to your friend, who paste and adds it.</li>
As a result: Your friend is not sticky.<p>
</ol><p>
<i>Alternatively: Add-Sticky-Modus: <b>Key Exchange</b> via IP Connection</i><p><ol>
<li>Add a listener. Forward the Port in your Router/Nat.</li>
<li>Send IP/Port to your friend. Add Neighbor.</li>
<li>Once connected, both users share the key via the context menu in the Neighbors IP-table.</li>
<li>Approve of new chat friends via the context menu in the Participants table: "Make Permanent Friends".</li>
As a result: Your friend is made a sticky Neighbor.<p>
</ol></body></html>
END
